# ildb

The ILDB - the Internet Legislative Database - is an API that allows users 
to pull specific legislators, all present congressmen and senators, 
specific bills or all bills.

## Legislator Collection [/api/legislators{?limit}]
Calling with no limit argument returns all legislators in the databse.

### List all legislators [GET]

+ Parameters
    + limit (number) - optional argument specifying the number of legislators to retrieve

