## Single legislator [/api/legislators/{legislator_id}]

+ Parameters
    + legislator_id (number) - ID of the legislator

### Get one legislator [GET]
Use the legislator id listed in the legislators table to retrieve that specific person.
+ Response 200 (application/json)

